{"tid":17886,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"2016 手機輻射排行榜：華為、蘋果手機輻射最高","createTime":"2016-12-02T04:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T16:45:14.000Z","uid":2339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db810c5458d6b1aa5fed1eff161ef3d669957f03","tid":17886,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:00:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.vtechgraphy.com/featured-news/2016-smartphone-sar-rating/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vtechgraphy.com%2Ffeatured-news%2F2016-smartphone-sar-rating%2F&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6gv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=fb007f0d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vtechgraphy.com/featured-news/2016-smartphone-sar-rating/</a><br />\n<br />\n說到輻射，相信不少人看到這兩個字臉色會立即變，要知道長期與輻射共處不單會讓身體出現不適，嚴重的話甚至會致癌或影響胎兒發育。好在為了大家的安全市面上幾乎所有手機在推出前都會經過測試以確保手機發出的輻射是屬於安全範圍內，但大家還是難免會好奇到底市面上新推出的手機，哪一部發出的電磁輻射量最高，而哪一部是最安全的呢？趕快來看看最新調查報告吧！<br />\n<br />\n根據法國 PhanDroid 網站最新的測試報告顯示，Top 3 發出最高電磁輻射量的智能手機由華為與蘋果包辦，其中以華為手機最「威風」，<span style=\"color: red;\">旗下的 Honor 8 以及華為 P9 竟然包辦了前二名，直接把一向名列前茅的蘋果 iPhone 7 給比下去，不少網友看到這不禁開玩笑說「華為這回終於如願把蘋果給拿下了」</span>！值得一提的是，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>蘋果今年推出的 3 部新機包括 iPhone 7、iPhone 7 Plus 以及 iPhone SE 紛紛都高調入榜，看來實力雄厚的蘋果還是「技高一籌」的。</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTop 10 發出最高電磁輻射量的智能手機<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2016/11/29/161129-27553-3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F161129-27553-3.png&h=f18ac5f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那哪一部 2016 年推出的智能手機是最安全的呢？或許您沒想到竟然是它！對，在經歷了爆炸門事件後，Samsung 終於有好消息傳出，旗下年頭推出的 Galaxy S7 Edge 不單成為今年輻射量最低的智能手機，而 Top 10 最低輻射榜裡 Samsung 竟然有 4 部手機入榜，表現真的讓人格外驚喜。此外，大家熟悉的 Asus Zenfone 3、OnePlus 3 以及 HTC 10 也紛紛入榜，名列「最安全」手機前十。<br />\n<br />\nTop 10 發出最低電磁輻射量的智能手機<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2016/11/29/161129-27553-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F161129-27553-2.png&h=52227eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不知您會否拿以上的輻射數據作為未來購買新手機的重要考量之一呢？需再次提醒大家的是，以上入榜的手機無論輻射最高或低其實都符合國際安全標準，這意味著它對人體的「傷害」仍屬於安全範圍內。"},{"pid":"9e53c6b036e664a08fe7b0f8ed828123dc83744c","tid":17886,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7debc5a9992f1abfd9cc076c4c21cbb6b1dc9309","tid":17886,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T07:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1899bf109f9fca3900eae78f393412c0e0a90490","tid":17886,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T07:38:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"618660277473f880cf0536462c6272b728e28052","tid":17886,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T07:38:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f5a57cb8540236d9d95da3ded509d6356a6aafd","tid":17886,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:05:19.000Z","msg":"三叔學人講最安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ef1f10ff05f78417c4a845516ee4540ec00a78","tid":17886,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:09:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三叔學人講最安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三叔係呢方面一直都做得幾好"},{"pid":"eb908eb0a7195ba997e67ad49413796e532d074d","tid":17886,"uid":45252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:11:40.000Z","msg":"金屬會擋訊息，所以金屬機身既電話要加大功率先去到其他電話既水平<br />\n所以iphone...."},{"pid":"243f613ba6bbfb1526d43d59826f3a6f9016a98f","tid":17886,"uid":7886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":